President Jacob Zuma wished Archbishop Emeritus Desmond Tutu a joyful birthday good health and comfort . Tutu turns 85 on Friday.Zuma said: Archbishop Emeritus Tutu has contributed immensely to the freedom and democratic dispensation we achieved as a country. He continues to inspire the nation and the world in the promotion of human rights justice and the wellbeing of all especially the poor. We wish him a joyful birthday good health and comfort and urge the nation to keep him and his family in their thoughts and prayers. 